item.title: Covid-19 Dashboard
item.description: This is the Covid-19 dashboard. The data is extracted from Worldometers as at 26 July 2021, 2pm Malaysia time. This interactive dashboard will display the Total cases, Active cases, Total death, Total recovered and Serious cases of Covid-19 worldwide. Interactive Covid-19 Dashboard The latest Covid-19 dataset can be found using this link: https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/ The demonstration can be assessed using this link: https://github.com/Alvinygno/Covid-19
